         I was soloing in SD at 44, but had to zone to the grey a good number of times.  After you get your 49 pet, it's a joke.  Non-stop killing my brother.  I cant suggest strongly enough.. DONT ZONE INTO GRIEGS!  That is an ugly beatdown waiting to happen.  Use the grey zone.  You need to pay attention when zoning because a lot of people will drop those nasty stone fiends from the grey at the end of the tunnel zoning into SD.  If that happens, immediate zone back to SD, and FD as you come out.</P><P>P.S. ALWAYS keep DMF up!</P><P> <a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
